        {
            "text": "One day, mama bought different fruits.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8025.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "\"When can we have some fruit?\" we asked.\n\"We will eat the fruit tonight,\" said mama.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8032.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "My brother Rahim is greedy.\nHe tasted all the fruit. He ate a lot of it.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8029.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "\"Look at what Rahim did!\" shouted my little brother.\n\"Rahim is naughty and selfish,\" I said.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8027.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Mama was angry with Rahim.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8023.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "We were also angry with Rahim.\nBut Rahim was not sorry.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8024.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "\"Are you going to punish Rahim?\" asked little brother.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8030.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "\"Rahim, you will be sorry soon,\" warned mama.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8033.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Rahim started feeling unwell.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8031.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "\"My stomach is painful,\" whispered Rahim.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8034.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Mama knew why Rahim was sick.\n\"The fruit is punishing Rahim,\" she thought.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8035.png"
        },
        {
            "text": "Later, Rahim said sorry to us.\u00a0\"I will never be so greedy again,\" he promised.\nWe believed him.",
            "imagePath": "assets/topic/asb/8036.png"
        },
        {
